<DOCNO> LA092794-0055 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 083097 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
September 27, 1994, Tuesday, Home Edition 
</P>
