Southern Sections. 05,21,07,06,06,04 School Sect. Div. Rec. LW 1. Bishop Amat 
SS I 3-0 1 2. Los Alamitos SS I 3-0 2 3. Mater Dei SS I 3-0 3 4. Loyola SS I 
