<HEADLINE>
<P>
FRAGILE ECONOMY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 I am an operator of a business in Ventura as well as a voter, and I am 
extremely concerned about the possible closure of Point Mugu and Port Hueneme 
military bases in Ventura County due to the Base Realignment and Closure 
(BRAC-95) process enacted by Congress. 
