<P>
MOVED TO ACTION 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 On Sept. 7, a letter published in this paper stated that I was conned into 
signing the Weldon Canyon landfill petition. 
</P>
<P>
 For the writer's information, I carried the petition as a volunteer. I am not 
totally oblivious to what has been happening for years in regards to trash 
