<HEADLINE>
<P>
THE MELDING AMERICAS; A SMALL WORLD AFTER ALL 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 American culture has a hold on Latin America, and the United States is fertile 
ground for Central and South American imports and influences. Their rich 
histories and distinctive fads keep bringing the hemisphere's nations closer. 
</P>
