SONORA CENTER CLARK SELECTS SAN JOSE STATE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Craig Clark, a senior center at Sonora High School, has made an oral 
commitment to play basketball at San Jose State, Sonora Coach Mike Murphy said 
Monday. 
</P>
<P>
